{{Orphan|date=January 2017}}
The '''Kindler Literature encyclopedia''' (in German: Das Kindler Literatur Lexikon) is an [[encyclopedia]] released in Germany covering information about [[world literature]]. Its first edition was released from 1965 to 1972 (7 volumes).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.derkindler.de/benutzungshinweise/vorwort-kindler-2009/|title=Vorwort Kindler 2009 - derkindlers Webseite!|publisher=}}</ref> Its second and third edition were distributed from 1988–1992 (20 volumes) and in 2009 (18 volumes).<ref>
https://www.welt.de/kultur/article4830514/Kindlers-Literatur-Lexikon-schlaegt-locker-Wikipedia.html
</ref> In 1999 a CD-ROM version was released.

For the first release the publisher Helmut Kindler started to translate articles from the Italian encyclopedia "Dizionario Letterario Bompiani". Additionally Kindler hired a crew to wrote articles on their own. As the first edition started as a translation, its primary focus was romanesque literature. With the second edition the former translations were to be rewritten. After a lot of nation building in between the 2. and 3. edition, some countries literature were merged (e.g. Russia and Ukraine).

In 2009 the German newspaper ''[[Die Welt]]'' called the Kindler superior to Wikipedia articles.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.welt.de/kultur/article4830514/Kindlers-Literatur-Lexikon-schlaegt-locker-Wikipedia.html|title=Kindlers Literatur-Lexikon schlägt locker Wikipedia: Nachschlagewerk - WELT|website=DIE WELT|access-date=2017-01-22}}
</ref> From all the articles in the 2009 edition, the half was newly rewritten. An Online version went live at the same time.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.literaturblatt.de/heftarchiv/heftarchiv-2009/52009-inhaltsverzeichnis-der-gedruckten-ausgabe/mit-18-baenden-um-die-welt-das-neue-kindlers-literatur-lexikon.html|title=literaturblatt: Mit 18 Bänden um die Welt – das neue Kindlers Literatur Lexikon|last=|first=|date=|website=www.literaturblatt.de|publisher=|language=de|access-date=2017-01-22}}
</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.derkindler.de/benutzungshinweise/vorwort-kindler-2009/|title=Vorwort Kindler 2009 - derkindlers Webseite!|website=www.derkindler.de|language=de-DE|access-date=2017-01-22}}
</ref>

